==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Highway
<hw>High"way`</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>A road or way open
to the use of the public, especially a paved main road or thoroughfare
between towns; in the latter sense it contrasts with <contr>local
street</contr>; <as>as, on the <ex>highways</ex> and
byways</as>.</def></p>

<p><syn><b>Syn.</b> -- Way; road; path; course.</syn>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Highwayman</ent>⟦br⟧
